title: Balenciaga Mini Rodeo Bag
description: Balenciaga mini Rodeo 2way bag in black smooth calfskin leather. Featuring gold-tone hardware, a leather top handle, two exterior pockets at back and button closure on the sides. The turn-lock closure opens to a black leather interior with two compartments and a patch pocket. Approximate dimensions: 23cm(L) x 17cm(H) x 9cm(D), 12cm handle drop & 69cm detachable strap drop. Accompanied by detachable clochette, keyring & dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity.(Pre-owned).
